Background Information:


Robertson Opportunity Capital LLC »
Robertson Opportunity Capital employs a fundamental, bottom-up, research-driven approach to identify and evaluate suitable securities. The firm uses a concentrated, all-cap, value-based long/short strategy. They are investors, rather than speculators, seeking to exploit neglected or misunderstood situations. Robertson also looks across entire capital structure for the best risk/reward opportunities.




