Colfax Corporation presently has a consensus target price of $42.86, indicating a potential upside of 2.11%. Graco has a consensus target price of $101.00, indicating a potential downside of 6.43%. Given Colfax Corporation’s stronger consensus rating and  higher possible upside, analysts plainly believe Colfax Corporation is more favorable than Graco.
