How do I update this listing?




                                             Robertson Opportunity Capital is based out of Dallas. Robertson Opportunity Capital is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $201,480,701 (Form ADV from 2017-03-31).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $154,459,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 53.33%. Robertson Opportunity Capital's largest holding is Copart Inc. with shares held of 225,376.  Robertson Opportunity Capital has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 45 13F filings in our database for Robertson Opportunity Capital. 
                                           






